ing • Score analysis • Progress updates 14. Key Features of ARK • Small batch size (15–20 students) • Structured academic system • Weekly testing discipline • Personalized mentoring • Performance analytics • Parent transparency 15. Location ARK Learning Arena is located at: 2/A, 132, Bazar Line Ramapuram, St. Thomas Mount Chennai – 600016 The institute is easily accessible from major areas in Chennai. 16. Contact Details Phone / WhatsApp: +91 76393 99217 Email: info@tuitionwithark.com Website: tuitionwithark.com 17. Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ) Q: What makes ARK different from other coaching centers? ARK follows a structured system with testing, analytics, and mentoring instead of regular tuition methods. Q: Do you focus on concepts or memorization? ARK focuses on concept clarity and application-based learning. Q: Do you provide demo classes? ARK provides a free Academic Diagnostic Assessment instead of demo classes. Q: What is the batch size? Each batch has 15–20 students for better attention. Q: Do you provide NEET coaching? Yes, ARK provides a structured NEET coaching program. Q: How do you track student progress? Through weekly tests, monthly exams, analytics, and reports. Q: Do you support weak students? Yes, ARK provides remedial sessions and personalized mentoring.", "tf": {"free": 2, "evaluation": 1, "system": 4, "identifies": 1, "current": 1, "academic": 4, "level": 1, "highlights": 1, "strengths": 1, "weaknesses": 1, "provides": 4, "personalized": 3, "improvement": 1, "plan": 1, "ada": 2, "counselling": 2, "session": 2, "program": 3, "recommendation": 1, "admission": 2, "guidance": 1, "12": 1, "process": 1, "steps": 1, "book": 1, "diagnostic": 2, "assessment": 2, "attend": 2, "test": 1, "receive": 1, "performance": 3, "analysis": 2, "select": 1, "complete": 1, "registration": 1, "start": 1, "classes": 3, "13": 1, "parent": 2, "communication": 1, "ark": 9, "ensures": 1, "transparency": 2, "monthly": 2, "reports": 2, "attendance": 1, "tracking": 1, "scor